%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor DQM as DEQA Manager

participant UI as DEQA Approval UI
participant BFF as Quality Management BFF
participant ORCH@{ "type":"boundary", "alias":"Journey Orchestrator"}
participant DEQA as DEQA Management Service
participant NS as Notification Service
participant READDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}
participant PRIMARYDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}
participant KAFKA@{ "type": "queue", "alias": "Message Bus"}

DQM->>UI: Open DEQA request
UI->>BFF: Load DEQA request detail
BFF->>ORCH: Get DEQA request view
ORCH->>DEQA: Fetch request details
DEQA->>READDB: Read deqa_request, deqa_request_item, <br/>deqa_request_checklist, <br/>deqa_request_document
READDB-->>DEQA: Request detail
DEQA-->>ORCH: View response
ORCH-->>BFF: Response
BFF-->>UI: Show request and scheduling fields

alt Approve and assign lead
    DQM->>UI: Approve request and assign DEQA lead
    UI->>BFF: Submit approval
    BFF->>ORCH: Start DEQA approval flow
    ORCH->>DEQA: Approve request and assign lead
    DEQA->>PRIMARYDB: Update deqa_request (status = Ongoing,<br/> lead assigned, schedule saved)
    DEQA->>PRIMARYDB: Insert deqa_status_history
    PRIMARYDB-->>DEQA: Save success
    DEQA-->>ORCH: Approval success
    ORCH->>NS: Notify DEQA Lead
    ORCH->>KAFKA: Publish DEQARequestApproved Event
    ORCH-->>BFF: Success
    BFF-->>UI: Show approved/ongoing state
else Send Back
    DQM->>UI: Send back request
    UI->>BFF: Submit send back
    BFF->>ORCH: Start send back flow
    ORCH->>DEQA: Update request to Sent Back
    DEQA->>PRIMARYDB: Update deqa_request <br/>(status = Sent Back)
    DEQA->>PRIMARYDB: Insert deqa_status_history
    PRIMARYDB-->>DEQA: Save success
    DEQA-->>ORCH: Send back success
    ORCH->>NS: Notify Project Manager
    ORCH->>KAFKA: Publish DEQARequestSentBack Event
    ORCH-->>BFF: Success
    BFF-->>UI: Show sent back state
end
